/semperplugins.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/wordpress-seo-checklist-2-300x88.jpg 300w, https://semperplugins.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/wordpress-seo-checklist-2-768x226.jpg 768w, https://semperplugins.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/wordpress-seo-checklist-2-1024x301.jpg 1024w, https://semperplugins.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/wordpress-seo-checklist-2-850x250.jpg 850w, https://semperplugins.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/wordpress-seo-checklist-2-100x29.jpg 100w, https://semperplugins.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/wordpress-seo-checklist-2-150x44.jpg 150w, https://semperplugins.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/wordpress-seo-checklist-2-200x59.jpg 200w, https://semperplugins.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/wordpress-seo-checklist-2-450x132.jpg 450w, https://semperplugins.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/wordpress-seo-checklist-2-600x177.jpg 600w, https://semperplugins.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/wordpress-seo-checklist-2-900x265.jpg 900w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1771px) 100vw, 1771px\" /></p>\\n<p>If you haven&#8217;t noticed, SEO has changed over the past months. Search engines맊onstantly update their algorithms which often makes it difficult to keep track of the latest best practices. We&#8217;ll help you많et started on implementing an effective strategy and getting your site to the top.</p>\\n<p>Whether youre setting up a new site or optimizing a current one, this checklist contains everything you need to know.</p>\\n<p>Let뗩 start망ith three vital changes that have dramatically affectedSEO말n 2016.</p>\\n<h2>Mobile Dominates</h2>\\n<p>Mobile has become more important than desktop:<a href=\"http://searchengineland.com/its-official-google-says-more-searches-now-on-mobile-than-on-desktop-220369\" target=\"_blank\">over 50 percent of all Google searches queries are now performed맖n mobile devices</a>. This means that we&#8217;ll맏ave to prioritize mobile from now on when it comes to SEO and web development. It&#8217;s of the utmost importance that your망ebsite is responsive 늡caling content마nd built망ith mobile users in mind.</p>\\n<h2>Social Matters More</h2>\\n<p>Social media content is becoming an equal to website content at a fast rate. Search engines are now indexing and ranking social media pages, so it is inevitable that website content and social content will hold the similar망eight in rankings in the near future. This means that businesses should claim their social pages, become more active on their relevant social networks and engage their audience.</p>\\n<h2>Video Conquers The Web</h2>\\n<p>Video is now key to마ny branding or맔arketing strategy; perhaps because it is more engaging and immersive than any other form of content. This is the time to start taking마dvantage of video and reach your audience in creative ways.</p>\\n<p>Now let뗩 look at our SEO checklist.</p>\\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:50:\"https://semperplugins.com/seo-checklist-2016/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"\\n		\\n		\\n		\\n		\\n		\\n				\\n\\n		\\n		\\n				\\n			\\n		\\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"Security Update for All in One SEO Pack\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"https://semperplugins.com/security-update-for-all-in-one-seo-pack/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:75:\"https://semperplugins.com/security-update-for-all-in-one-seo-pack/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 12 Jul 2016 23:21:56 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"Blog\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"http://semperplugins.com/?p=2391\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:398:\"Semper Plugins마nnounces the release of All in One SEO Pack 2.3.8, and All in One SEO Pack Pro 2.4.8, a security update to previous releases. We recommend that users of All in One SEO and All in One SEO Pack<span class=\"ellipsis\">&#8230;</span><div class=\"read-more\"><a href=\"https://semperplugins.com/security-update-for-all-in-one-seo-pack/\">Read more &#8250;</a></div><!-- end of .read-more -->\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Michael Torbert\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2633:\"<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Semper Plugins마nnounces the release of <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/all-in-one-seo-pack/\" target=\"_blank\">All in One SEO Pack</a> 2.3.8, and <a href=\"http://semperplugins.com/all-in-one-seo-pack-pro-version/?loc=sec_update_post\">All in One SEO Pack Pro</a> 2.4.8, a security update to previous releases. We recommend that users of All in One SEO and All in One SEO Pack Pro upgrade as soon as they are able to do so.</span></p>\\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">This release closes a security vulnerability first identified by <span class=\"s2\"><a href=\"https://sumofpwn.nl/advisory/2016/persistent_cross_site_scripting_in_all_in_one_seo_pack_wordpress_plugin.html\">David Vaartjes</a></span>in a security hackathon last week. After notifying us, we immediately issued 2.3.7 to patch the issue마nd protect our customers, which we estimate to have affected less than 0.5% of our customer base.</span></p>\\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Meanwhile, we sought out any similar vulnerabilities in our code base, and asked <a href=\"https://www.wordfence.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"s2\">WordFence</span></a>, who helped us identify an additional case, to verify our fix, which they have.</span></p>\\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">As a third precautionary step, we are currently undergoing independent audits from WordFence,<a href=\"https://sucuri.net/\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"s2\">Sucuri</span></a> and <a href=\"http://coveredwebservices.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"s2\">Mark Jacquith</span></a>, the three most trusted names in WordPress security. While one source might be sufficient, we are going above and beyond in our due diligence to ensure that our codebase and our customers are as secure as possible.</span></p>\\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Although All in One SEO Pack continues to be your best SEO solution for WordPress, bolstered by almost 30 million downloads and 5 million active users, we expect future updates in the coming months as we adopt any recommendations from our security audits to harden our codebase. As with any plugin, theme or WordPress core, we recommend staying up to date with updates.</span></p>\\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">We want to thank David Vaartjes맍or their responsible reporting. As noted above, a release was issued immediately for the above issue (2.3.7) which we believe would only have been able to affect 0.5% or less of our users. Now we&#8217;ve gone even further, scouring our code base for potential vulnerabilities마nd issuing an additional release today (2.3.8) which WordFence has verified.</span></p>\\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:71:\"https://semperplugins.com/security-update-for-all-in-one-seo-pack/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"4\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"href\";s:31:\"https://semperplugins.com/feed/\";s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:44:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/\";a:2:{s:12:\"updatePeriod\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"hourly\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:15:\"updateFrequency\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}}}}}}s:4:\"type\";i:128;s:7:\"headers\";O:42:\"Requests_Utility_CaseInsensitiveDictionary\":1:{s:7:\"\\0*\\0data\";a:15:{s:6:\"server\";s:5:\"nginx\";s:4:\"date\";s:29:\"M